        {
            "_id": "051PuLaSpaUM4n6y",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Draw Power",
            "sort": 300000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "reaction"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The unspooled vestige is hit by a ranged weapon that uses charges and has at least 1 charge remaining in its battery</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The unspooled vestige pulls energy from the weapon, causing it to expend an additional charge.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "qC77y0fTeUuUG9d5",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Slip Out of Reality",
            "sort": 400000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>At the end of its turn, the unspooled vestige must attempt a @Check[flat|dc:11]. On a failure, it slips slightly out of reality. It takes @Damage[1d4[force]] damage, and becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Concealed] until the start of its next turn.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "0h9gOyR14FpTY68o",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Entanglement",
            "sort": 500000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A unspooled vestige filament becomes entangled with a creature it hits. The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Grabbed]; they're not @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized], but they can't move beyond the range of the unspooled vestige's filament. The unspooled vestige can attempt to [[/act reposition]] each entangled creature with a single Athletics check, which they compare against each creature's Fortitude DC. Doing so only counts as one attempt for the unspooled vestige's multiple attack penalty. The DC to [[/act escape dc=18]] is 18, or a creature can sever the filament with a Strike against AC 15 that deals at least 3 slashing damage. This deals no damage to the unspooled vestige. The unspooled vestige can move without ending the entanglement as long as the creature remains within the filament's range.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "MVF9DHxKXeHjV01Q",
            "img": "systems/sf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Unspool",
            "sort": 600000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The fabric of the creature's reality begins to fray. The unspooled vestige must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:16] save. On a failure it takes @Damage[1d4[force]] damage, or @Damage[1d6[force]] damage on a critical failure.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        }
